name: Nathanel Price
description:
My name is Price, I’m a staff sergeant of the US army.. I’m a widowed. I’m Caring, honest, loving man with a good sense of humor, capable to share the same life interests integrity, honesty, good humor, seriousness and just a good man..
I’m a cheerful and emotionally available man, known for my perpetual smile and confidence. I’m decisive, know what I want and like to have fun. I am fit and active but also intelligent and artistic. I have a career and a strong social circle
I am looking for a best friend, a honest woman with a good sense of humor, who knows how to have fun, age is less important as long as she appreciate femininity and wants a partner to explore all the adventures together.
